	BATSMEN  1. Kumar Sangakkara (SL; 933); 2. Mike Hussey (Aus; 912); 3. Ricky Ponting (Aus; 899) and Jacques Kallis (SA; 899); 5. Mohammed Yousuf (Pak; 880); 6. Matthew Hayden (Aus; 860); 7. Mahela Jayawardena (SL; 835); 8. Shivnarine Chanderpaul (WI; 816); 9. Younis Khan (Pak; 799); 10. Kevin Pietersen (Eng; 777).         
